questions.question: Do you have any direct or indirect financial ownership or partial ownership in any business that sells cigarettes or does business with R. J. Reynolds?

Do you, in any direct or indirect way, financially benefit from any retail business or other business that sells cigarettes or does business with R. J. Reynolds?
